Set up passthrough:
https://pve.proxmox.com/wiki/Passthrough_Physical_Disk_to_Virtual_Machine_(VM)

It gives you a way to set up the drive on a scsi drive with specific ID:
qm set 101 -scsi1 /dev/disk/by-id/ata-MAXTOR_STM3500630AS_9QG7B15T-part1
